  id: 2
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD b\xE1c s\u0129 #2"
  category: 0
  content: "T\u1EC7 th\u1EADt, thu\u1ED1c kh\xF4ng nh\u01B0 k\xEC v\u1ECDng r\u1ED3i
    !!! H\u1EC5 ai ti\u1EBFp x\xFAc v\u1EDBi m\u1EA5y \u0111\u1EE9a th\u1EED thu\u1ED1c
    \u0111\u1EC1u b\u1ECB c\xE0o v\xE0 bi\u1EBFn th\xE0nh qu\xE1i v\u1EADt. C\xF2n
    th\u1EB1ng th\u1EED \u0111\u1EA7u ti\xEAn sao n\xF3 c\xE0ng ng\xE0y c\xE0ng to
    \u1EA5y nh\u1EC9 ? Trong th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1 xu\u1EA5t hi\u1EC7n th\xEAm nhi\u1EC1u
    ca nhi\u1EC5m b\u1EC7nh k\xEC l\u1EA1, gi\u1ED1ng y chang m\u1EA5y \u0111\u1EE9a
    th\u1EED thu\u1ED1c c\u1EE7a m\xECnh. Ch\u1EAFc m\xECnh n\xEAn r\u1EDDi kh\u1ECFi
    th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1 n\xE0y s\u1EDBm. Sau khi ho\xE0n th\xE0nh ph\u01B0\u01A1ng
    thu\u1ED1c b\u1EA5t t\u1EED n\xE0y, m\xECnh s\u1EBD gi\xE0u to. B\xE1c s\u0129
    Edward."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
